      "disable": "<p>@Check[type:religion|dc:35] (Master) to calm the spirits within the bell or dispel magic (7th level; counteract DC 31) to counteract the bell.</p>",
      "description": "<p>An immense bell that rises up from the ground to unleash two deafening peals to the castle as shrieking spirits race around the room in indignant fury.</p><hr /><h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p>The belfry's signal bell — one peal once meant muster, two meant attack. The haunt remembers the second kind.</p>",
      "reset": "<p>The bell resets after 1 hour.</p>",
